flowchart TD
  A[Signed-in person reaches agreements status page] --> B[Load unaccepted required registration agreements]
  B --> C{Any pending onboarding agreements?}
  C -- No --> D[Redirect to stored return path]
  C -- Yes --> E[Render agreement cards with locked checkboxes]
  E --> F[Person opens agreement modal]
  F --> G[Turbo frame loads agreement content]
  G --> H{Scrolled through full agreement?}
  H -- No --> I[Checkbox remains locked]
  H -- Yes --> J[Stimulus unlocks matching checkbox]
  J --> K[Person checks all remaining agreements]
  K --> L[Submit agreements status form]
  L --> M[Recorder stores acceptance audit entries]
  M --> N[Redirect to return path or profile]
